    "We designed this user study following the research ethics guidelines of our affiliated organization.",
    "We prepared eight themes for decision-making tasks and one theme for practice tasks.",
    "The themes were prepared from the website of the National Association of Debate in Education, Japan.",
    "We selected the frequently used nine themes in debate competitions for high school students in Japan, as listed in Table 1.",
    "As presented in Table 1, the impressions of participants indicated their unfamiliarity with most themes on average."
